	function initShareDocument() {
    const mediaPlatforms = document.querySelectorAll(
      '[data-type="facebook"], [data-type="twitter"], [data-type="linkedin"], [data-type="instagram"]'
    );
    const handlePost = (media) => {
      const pageURL = encodeURIComponent(window.location.href);
      switch (media) {
        case 'facebook':
          const facebookShareUrl = `https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=${pageURL}`;
          window.open(
            facebookShareUrl,
            'MsgWindow',
            'toolbar=no,status=no,menubar=no,location=center,scrollbars=no,resizable=no,height=500,width=657'
          );
          break;
        case 'twitter':
          const twitterShareUrl = `https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=${pageURL}`;
          window.open(
            twitterShareUrl,
            'sharer',
            'toolbar=no,status=no,menubar=no,location=center,scrollbars=no,resizable=no,height=500,width=657'
          );
          break;
        case 'linkedin':
          const linkedinShareUrl = `http://www.linkedin.com/shareArticle?mini=true&url=${pageURL}`;
          window.open(
            linkedinShareUrl,
            'MsgWindow',
            'toolbar=no,status=no,menubar=no,location=center,scrollbars=no,resizable=no,height=500,width=657'
          );
          break;
        case 'instagram':
          const instagramShareUrl = `https://www.instagram.com/?url=${pageURL}`;
          window.open(
            instagramShareUrl,
            'MsgWindow',
            'toolbar=no,status=no,menubar=no,location=center,scrollbars=no,resizable=no,height=500,width=657'
          );
          break;
        default:
          console.warn('Unsupported data-type:', media);
          break;
      }
    };
    mediaPlatforms.forEach((media) => {
      media.addEventListener('click', (event) => {
        event.preventDefault();
        handlePost(media.getAttribute('data-type'));
      });
    });
  }
  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', initShareDocument);

	function initShareDocument() {
    const mediaPlatforms = document.querySelectorAll(
      '[data-type="facebook"], [data-type="twitter"], [data-type="linkedin"], [data-type="instagram"]'
    );
    const handlePost = (media) => {
      const pageURL = encodeURIComponent(window.location.href);
      switch (media) {
        case 'facebook':
          const facebookShareUrl = `https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=${pageURL}`;
          window.open(
            facebookShareUrl,
            'MsgWindow',
            'toolbar=no,status=no,menubar=no,location=center,scrollbars=no,resizable=no,height=500,width=657'
          );
          break;
        case 'twitter':
          const twitterShareUrl = `https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=${pageURL}`;
          window.open(
            twitterShareUrl,
            'sharer',
            'toolbar=no,status=no,menubar=no,location=center,scrollbars=no,resizable=no,height=500,width=657'
          );
          break;
        case 'linkedin':
          const linkedinShareUrl = `http://www.linkedin.com/shareArticle?mini=true&url=${pageURL}`;
          window.open(
            linkedinShareUrl,
            'MsgWindow',
            'toolbar=no,status=no,menubar=no,location=center,scrollbars=no,resizable=no,height=500,width=657'
          );
          break;
        case 'instagram':
          const instagramShareUrl = `https://www.instagram.com/?url=${pageURL}`;
          window.open(
            instagramShareUrl,
            'MsgWindow',
            'toolbar=no,status=no,menubar=no,location=center,scrollbars=no,resizable=no,height=500,width=657'
          );
          break;
        default:
          console.warn('Unsupported data-type:', media);
          break;
      }
    };
    mediaPlatforms.forEach((media) => {
      media.addEventListener('click', (event) => {
        event.preventDefault();
        handlePost(media.getAttribute('data-type'));
      });
    });
  }
  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', initShareDocument);

    input[type="radio"][custom="radio"] {
        appearance: none;
        -webkit-appearance: none;
        -moz-appearance: none;
        min-width: 20px;
        width: 20px;
        height: 20px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.64);
        border-radius: 50%;
        cursor: pointer;
        position: relative;
    }

    /* Default inner dot (when not checked) */
    input[type="radio"][custom="radio"]::after {
        content: "";
        width: 6px;
        height: 6px;
        background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.20);
        border-radius: 50%;
        position: absolute;
        top: 50%;
        left: 50%;
        transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    }

    /* Inner dot when checked */
    input[type="radio"][custom="radio"]:checked::after {
        background: #183FE1;
        width: 14px;
        height: 14px;
    }

    /* 🔹 Mobile styles (below 575px) */
    @media (max-width: 575px) {
        input[type="radio"][custom="radio"] {
            width: 16px;
            height: 16px;
            min-width: 16px;
        }

        input[type="radio"][custom="radio"]::after {
            width: 6px;
            /* keep small dot when unchecked */
